title: Ducktales Remastered /w Update1 *OSX/Wine*
description:
Ducktales Remastered (and REPACKAGED) /w Update1 included - Now available on OSX too.

Installation package that extracts DT:Re into your personal applications directory (~/Applications) so no root access needed or anything.

Just click and play.

Screen resolution is set to 1280*1024 by default, so adjust it as you see fit within game options.

Please note. This is a Wine Port, served as is. More than likely to contain bugs and errors.
